name: Yor Forger - Innocent Housewife version - TI Embedding by Corneo
description:
This is a textual inversion embedding for Yor Forger / Yor Briar from Spy x Family in her usual housewife outfit.

Despite a few attempts to improve the hair colour, it keeps coming out dark green rather than black so you probably want an emphasised black_hair tag along with this. Otherwise I'm quite happy with how it turned out (finally got the eyes right), but this one might be a bit too trained on the clothes making it hard to change them to something else (though changing clip skip from 2 will do that).

Example images created using my 7th Heaven mix https://civitai.com/models/4669/corneos-7th-heaven-mix

Check out my other civitai models for more characters and sex positions! https://civitai.com/user/Master_Corneo

If you enjoy this embed, I genuinely love seeing your creations with it - you can attach them to a review if you're not aware (but not comments sadly)!
